---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 学习
description: 主题学习笔记
---

<section class="section">
  <h2 class="section-title">学习</h2>
  <p class="card-desc">这里是主题式学习笔记：概念框架 + 关键术语 + 常见误区，方便快速回忆与对外讲解。</p>
  <div class="card-grid">
    {% for note in collections.learningList %}
      <article class="card">
        <a class="card-link" href="{{ note.url }}">
          <h3 class="card-title">{{ note.data.title }}</h3>
          {% if note.data.description %}
            <p class="card-desc">{{ note.data.description }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </a>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
